  <refnamediv>
    <refname>eolfix</refname>

    <refpurpose>command line <acronym>EOL</acronym> correction utility</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <cmdsynopsis>
      <command>eolfix</command>

      <arg><option><replaceable>&lt;option(s)&gt;</replaceable></option></arg>

      <arg><option><replaceable>&lt;file(s)&gt;</replaceable></option></arg>

    </cmdsynopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

  <refsect1 id="introduction">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>eolfix is a command line utility to query and correct end-of-line (EOL) characters in ASCII text files.</para>
  </refsect1>

